Kilolock — vendored Terraform Plugin RPC protocol bindings
=============================================================

Purpose
-------

Kilolock's v1 refresh path speaks the Terraform Plugin RPC protocol
directly to provider binaries (see ADR 0005). The generated Go bindings
for that protocol live inside terraform-plugin-go's `internal/`
packages, which Go's package visibility rules forbid importing from
outside that module. This directory holds a copy.

